            <section ids="multipath" names="multipath">
                <title>Multipath</title>
                <paragraph>The X-IO ISE supports a multipath configuration, but multipath must be enabled
                    on the compute node (see <emphasis>ISE Storage Blade Best Practices Guide</emphasis>).
                    For more information, see <reference name="X-IO Document Library" refuri="http://xiostorage.com/document_library/">X-IO Document Library</reference>.</paragraph>
            </section>
            <section ids="volume-types" names="volume\ types">
